      "description": {
        "value": "<p>You cause a web of hardened vines to grow up out of the ground around a creature, protecting them from attacks. Each square adjacent to the target becomes difficult terrain for the duration of the spell, and the target gains resistance 10 to slashing and bludgeoning damage as long as they stay in the same square. After the spell has blocked 30 damage, it ends immediately.\n<p>Increase the resistance granted by 2, and the total amount blocked by 10.\n</p>"
